	<h4>There was once such a girl</h4>
	<p>Once upon a time, not so long ago, there was just such a girl. All of 17, she fell for the handsome prince who turned out, like all the other princes, to be a toad. And like most girls, she wished and wished for the toad to turn back into the prince; but he never did. True to most toads, he hopped off with someone younger and took everything with him - except his princess bride. And in her tears, poured into the magical pond, she wished a wish that all tossed aside princesses wish./p>
        <p style="text-align:center">I wish I may, I wish I might...why can't I have my own knight in shining armour come to rescue me?</p>
